>Description:
Dr. Scheme quits when it shouldn't.
C-m w should be disabled when the close menu item is grayed.
>How-To-Repeat:
Start drscheme -x
Click on the file menu and note that Close is grayed.
Close the file menu.
Type C-m w
When it asks if you want to quit or not, click cancel.
Wonder why drscheme quits anyway.
